      "verse_key": "14:1",
      "text_uthmani_tajweed": "ا<tajweed class=madda_necessary>لٓ</tajweed>ر‌ۚ كِتَ<tajweed class=madda_normal>ـٰ</tajweed>بٌ أَ<tajweed class=ikhafa>نز</tajweed>َلْنَ<tajweed class=madda_normal>ـٰ</tajweed>هُ إِلَيْكَ لِتُخْرِجَ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed><tajweed class=laam_shamsiyah>ل</tajweed><tajweed class=ghunnah>نّ</tajweed>َاسَ مِنَ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed><tajweed class=laam_shamsiyah>ل</tajweed>ظُّلُمَ<tajweed class=madda_normal>ـٰ</tajweed>تِ إِلَى <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed><tajweed class=laam_shamsiyah>ل</tajweed><tajweed class=ghunnah>نّ</tajweed>ُورِ بِإِذْنِ رَبِّهِمْ إِلَىٰ صِر<tajweed class=madda_normal>َٲ</tajweed>طِ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْعَزِيزِ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْحَم<tajweed class=madda_permissible>ِي</tajweed><tajweed class=qalaqah>د</tajweed>ِ <span class=end>١</span>"
