      "verse_key": "14:2",
      "text_uthmani_tajweed": "ٱللَّهِ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لَّذِى لَهُ<tajweed class=madda_normal>ۥ</tajweed> مَا فِى <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed><tajweed class=laam_shamsiyah>ل</tajweed>سَّمَ<tajweed class=madda_normal>ـٰ</tajweed>و<tajweed class=madda_normal>َٲ</tajweed>تِ وَمَا فِى <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْأَرْضِ‌ۗ وَوَيْ<tajweed class=idgham_wo_ghunnah>لٌ ل</tajweed>ِّلْكَ<tajweed class=madda_normal>ـٰ</tajweed>فِرِينَ مِنْ عَذَا<tajweed class=ikhafa>بٍ ش</tajweed>َد<tajweed class=madda_permissible>ِي</tajweed><tajweed class=qalaqah>د</tajweed>ٍ <span class=end>٢</span>"
